{"tid":2154860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（建立新香港？）台灣人口正式進入負成長時代！學者警告未來三年恐更糟","createTime":"2020-08-13T11:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T07:35:26.000Z","uid":66087,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e54c9031f2482cadc6601763e88ec9c9615d7d8c","tid":2154860,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1KR3Oc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1KR3Oc.jpg&h=a788a5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我國內政部最新統計，今年1~6月，台灣人口正式進入負成長時代！<br />\n<br />\n新生兒呱呱落地，帶來新希望。以往出生數大多比死亡數多。不過今年1到6月，出生人數只有79760人，死亡人數卻高達88555人，整整多出8795人。死大於生，確定人口負成長，刷新歷史紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n台大社會系教授 薛承泰：「出生量不到8萬，這是從1950年以來，中華民國在台灣以來，從來就沒有生過這那麼少的，這是第一個，第二個我們發現，我們講所謂的生不如死，死亡數比出生數要多。」<br />\n<br />\n不只生得少，還入不敷出，上半年從外國遷入8900多人，遷出人口卻多達1萬6千多人，也創下最差紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n今年結婚對數比去年少了6000對，這當中又有多少人會生小孩？還是未知數。<br />\n<br />\n台大社會系教授 薛承泰：「除了今年會破底，明年狀況可能好不到哪裡去，而後年呢？各位知道後年是哪一年？後年是虎年，所以又是另外一個很大的衝擊，看來今年情況不樂觀，明年可能也回不來，後年又肯定更糟糕。」<br />\n<br />\n不只今年，學者預估到虎年為止，人口將連續三年下降。中壯年的壓力越來越大，人口怎麼止跌回升，將成為政府一大難題。"},{"pid":"2d8d497763b007f3658feb4b567a1cab9bdbad76","tid":2154860,"uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"台灣愁緊人口減少<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以借呢個機會推動新香港計劃呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa10b9b48abfce7b15478fd56a5d5c69a249d50","tid":2154860,"uid":33437,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"城中的人想出去，<br />\n城外的人想衝進来。"},{"pid":"da7bfc130dd5703fe81e266b16bf6268e37ecd81","tid":2154860,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCEbjoz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCEbjoz.jpg&h=d3e4a482&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6dGGBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6dGGBW.jpg&h=d2efdb2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF9nq3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF9nq3M.jpg&h=0b444a17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSeuQvE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSeuQvE.jpg&h=a98d25aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛去台灣 溝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d2410750b1cccf194daa0112c195e421b8eb69","tid":2154860,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"到兔年龍年馬年就會多架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲傳統思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609bd8eb64a0e013aa4212e8a977d4e7cd0e6d49","tid":2154860,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"18d2410750b1cccf194daa0112c195e421b8eb69","tid":2154860,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"到兔年龍年馬年就會多架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲傳統思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1KR3Oc.jpg&amp;h=a788a5ee&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"2f54c5d1a6e59e73f2265568db04855613a1ee04","tid":2154860,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aa10b9b48abfce7b15478fd56a5d5c69a249d50","tid":2154860,"uid":33437,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"城中的人想出去，<br />\n城外的人想衝進来。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"有人辭官歸故里 有人漏夜趕科場"},{"pid":"abdf7803bef95531dfc263ca426c3d2e691c1a27","tid":2154860,"uid":165336,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"成個亞洲都有同樣既問題<